properties.Name: DunBradstreetBusinessRegistration
properties.Description: This section of the report contains a general company overview, as well as a business summary (with SIC codes, line of business, and history status), plus a credit capacity summary with the D&B Rating.

Columns.Name: DunsNumber
Columns.Description: Dun & Bradstreet (D&B) provides a D-U-N-S Number, a unique nine digit identification number, for each physical location of your business.

Columns.Name: ReportPurchaseDate
Columns.Description: The purchase date of the report.

Columns.Name: RegistrationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Registration.

Columns.Name: RegisteredName
Columns.Description: The name of the registered company.

Columns.Name: FiledAtCity
Columns.Description: The city that the registration was filed at.

Columns.Name: FiledAtState
Columns.Description: The state that the registration was filed at.

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetBusinessTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Dun Bradstreet Business Type.

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetCorporationTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Dun Bradstreet Corporation Type.
